description:
More details unspool on tangled web of Biden family lies. He's not a nice guy: Biden falsely smears border agents. Senator Ron Johnson joins Clay and Buck to discuss Biden's dismal approval rating, how the corrupt media and deep state rigged the 2020 election, the border disaster that will come with the lifting of Title 42, and the election battle in front of us. China cuts all gay references from Harry Potter movie, Hollywood silent. Twitter board to reject Musk offer?
